--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.3.1 (2020-05-15)
B: Remove duplicate curl section in CentOS 8 'php.ini' configuration file

* Version 1.3.0 (2020-05-12)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-01-30)
F: Add support for 'mysql.allow_local_infile' option (php_mysql_allow_local_infile)
F: Add support for 'mysqli.allow_local_infile' option (php_mysqli_allow_local_infile)

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-08-16)
F: Add support for 'max_input_vars' option (php_max_input_vars)

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-08-15)
F: Add support for 'curl.cainfo' option (php_curl_cainfo)

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-04-17)
F: Initial release
